arStrings.szText: 伊萊亞斯不在了，而我留了下來。
Strained, since chains are around her. But she's coming to a realization now. The more she fights against Andariel, the worse it gets. Projected, said during combat.
這就是我，我可以選擇自己的道路。

Less strained than before. She has come to a realization. The more she fights against Andariel, the worse it gets--so now she will accept what she is. Strong, confident ending. Projected, said during combat.
我不需要害怕或感到羞恥。
